A [[currency_exchange]] where bitcoins can be purchased by those in the U.S. using a credit or debit card.  For the article about the similarly-named Bitcoin mining operation, see [[Simplecoin.us]].

The bitcoin purchase price is adjusted relative to current market rates.

The service was launched on December 4th, 2011 (1.1).

